Besides #WordPress5,  JAMstack (Javascript, APIs, and Markup) complemented with
the like of Netlify can be a viable approach. https://jamstack.org/examples/

Don't get intimidated by Javascript, APIs, and Markup.
Let focus first on Markup. Markup allows you to (Re-purpose your content)
[https://www.portent.com/blog/content-strategy/content-with-github-markdown.htm].
